trans-unit.source: Defines objects used to fill the interiors of graphical shapes such as rectangles, ellipses, pies, polygons, and paths.
trans-unit.target: Definerer objekter som brukes til å fylle interiors grafiske figurer som rektangler, ellipser, sektordiagram, polygoner og baner.

trans-unit.source: This is an abstract base class and cannot be instantiated.
trans-unit.target: Dette er en abstrakt basisklasse og kan ikke startes.

trans-unit.source: To create a brush object, use classes derived from Brush, such as <xref:System.Drawing.SolidBrush>, <xref:System.Drawing.TextureBrush>, and <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.LinearGradientBrush>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil opprette et velgeren-objekt, kan du bruke klasser som er avledet fra velgeren, for eksempel <xref:System.Drawing.SolidBrush>, <xref:System.Drawing.TextureBrush>, og <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.LinearGradientBrush>.</xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.LinearGradientBrush> </xref:System.Drawing.TextureBrush> </xref:System.Drawing.SolidBrush>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Drawing.Brush"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Drawing.Brush"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, creates an exact copy of this <xref href="System.Drawing.Brush"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Når overstyrt i en avledet klasse, oppretter du en nøyaktig kopi av denne <xref href="System.Drawing.Brush"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The new <xref href="System.Drawing.Brush"></xref> that this method creates.
trans-unit.target: Den nye <xref href="System.Drawing.Brush"> </xref> som opprettes for denne metoden.

trans-unit.source: Releases all resources used by this <xref href="System.Drawing.Brush"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Frigir alle ressursene som brukes av dette <xref href="System.Drawing.Brush"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: Calling Dispose allows the resources used by this <xref:System.Drawing.Brush> object to be reallocated for other purposes.
trans-unit.target: Kaller avhending tillater ressursene som brukes av dette <xref:System.Drawing.Brush>objektet som tildeles på nytt til andre formål.</xref:System.Drawing.Brush>

trans-unit.source: Call Dispose when you are finished using the <xref:System.Drawing.Brush>.
trans-unit.target: Kall avhending når du er ferdig med <xref:System.Drawing.Brush>.</xref:System.Drawing.Brush>

trans-unit.source: The Dispose method leaves the <xref:System.Drawing.Brush> in an unusable state.
trans-unit.target: Fjerningsmetoden forlater den <xref:System.Drawing.Brush>i en ubrukelig tilstand.</xref:System.Drawing.Brush>

trans-unit.source: After calling Dispose, you must release all references to the <xref:System.Drawing.Brush> so the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.Drawing.Brush> was occupying.
trans-unit.target: Etter å avhending, må du frigi alle referanser til den <xref:System.Drawing.Brush>Slik saneringsoppsamlingen kan gjenvinne minnet som den <xref:System.Drawing.Brush>ble bruker.</xref:System.Drawing.Brush> </xref:System.Drawing.Brush>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [Rydder opp uforvaltede ressurser](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) og [implementere metoden fjerne](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Always call Dispose before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.Drawing.Brush>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Alltid kall fjerne før du slipper siste referanse til <xref:System.Drawing.Brush>.</xref:System.Drawing.Brush>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources it is using will not be freed until the garbage collector calls the <xref:System.Drawing.Brush> object's `Finalize` method.
trans-unit.target: Ellers ressurser den bruker vil ikke bli frigjort før saneringsoppsamling kall av <xref:System.Drawing.Brush>objektets `Finalize` metode.</xref:System.Drawing.Brush>

trans-unit.source: Releases the unmanaged resources used by the <xref href="System.Drawing.Brush"></xref> and optionally releases the managed resources.
trans-unit.target: Frigir uforvaltede ressursene som brukes av den <xref href="System.Drawing.Brush"> </xref> og eventuelt frigir administrerte ressurser.

trans-unit.source: This method is called by the public `Dispose()`method and the <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kalles av offentlig `Dispose()`metoden og <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>metode.</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>

trans-unit.source: `Dispose()` invokes the protected `Dispose(Boolean)` method with the `disposing` parameter set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: `Dispose()`Aktiverer den beskyttede `Dispose(Boolean)` metoden med den `disposing` parameteren satt til `true`.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> invokes `Dispose` with `disposing` set to `false`.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>aktiverer `Dispose` med `disposing` satt til `false`.</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>

trans-unit.source: When the `disposing` parameter is true, this method releases all resources held by any managed objects that this <xref:System.Drawing.Brush> references.
trans-unit.target: Når den `disposing` -parameteren er SANN, denne metoden Frigjør alle ressurser holdes av administrerte objekter som denne <xref:System.Drawing.Brush>referanser.</xref:System.Drawing.Brush>

trans-unit.source: This method invokes the `Dispose()` method of each referenced object.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden starter den `Dispose()` metode for hver referert objekt.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to release both managed and unmanaged resources; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> to release only unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>å frigjøre både administrerte og uforvaltede ressurser. <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> frigi bare uforvaltede ressurser.

trans-unit.source: Allows an object to try to free resources and perform other cleanup operations before it is reclaimed by garbage collection.
trans-unit.target: Gjør det mulig for et objekt å prøve å frigjøre ressurser og utføre andre operasjoner for opprydding før den er gode av datasanering.

trans-unit.source: In a derived class, sets a reference to a [!INCLUDE[ndptecgdiplus](~/add/includes/ndptecgdiplus-md.md)] brush object.
trans-unit.target: I en avledet klasse, angir du en referanse til en [!INCLUDE[ndptecgdiplus](~/add/includes/ndptecgdiplus-md.md)] velgeren objektet.

trans-unit.source: A pointer to the [!INCLUDE[ndptecgdiplus](~/add/includes/ndptecgdiplus-md.md)] brush object.
trans-unit.target: En peker til den [!INCLUDE[ndptecgdiplus](~/add/includes/ndptecgdiplus-md.md)] velgeren objektet.
